title: Flood mapping seeking Ministerial authorisation (Manningham City Council)
text: ( Source : Manningham City Council ) 30 September 2015 Manningham Council will be writing to the Minister for Planning to seek authorisation to implement the findings of a review of flood mapping of five local catchments within Manningham.
